tn"><div class="ex-icon">🟢</div><div class="ex-name">Swyftx</div></div> <div class="ex-btn"><div class="ex-icon">⚫</div><div class="ex-name">Ind. Reserve</div></div> <div class="ex-btn"><div class="ex-icon">🔐</div><div class="ex-name">Hardware Wallets</div></div> </div> <p style="font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);text-align:center;">+ Closed exchanges · Seed phrase recovery · ATO tax guide</p> </div> <!-- HOW IT WORKS --> <div class="pcard"> <div class="pcard-header"> <div class="pcard-icon ic-teal">🔓</div> <div> <div class="pcard-title">How Recovery Works</div> <div class="pcard-sub">Your crypto isn't gone — just locked</div> </div> </div> <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px;font-size:13px;"> <div style="display:flex;gap:10px;align-items:flex-start;padding:10px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.03);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;"> <span style="color:var(--teal);font-weight:800;font-size:16px;">1</span> <div><strong style="color:var(--white);display:block;">Gather your documents</strong><span style="color:var(--muted);">Photo ID, email address, account details</span></div> </div> <div style="display:flex;gap:10px;align-items:flex-start;padding:10px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.03);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;"> <span style="color:var(--teal);font-weight:800;font-size:16px;">2</span> <div><strong style="color:var(--white);display:block;">Follow the exchange guide</strong><span style="color:var(--muted);">Each exchange has its own recovery process</span></div> </div> <div style="display:flex;gap:10px;align-items:flex-start;padding:10px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.03);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;"> <span style="color:var(--teal);font-weight:800;font-size:16px;">3</span> <div><strong style="color:var(--white);display:block;">Regain your access</strong><span style="color:var(--muted);">Exchange verifies your identity and restores access</span></div> </div> </div> </div> <!-- PREMIUM FULL WIDTH --> <div class="pcard pcard-full" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(0,201,167,0.08),rgba(247,147,26,0.06));border-color:rgba(0,201,167,0.3);"> <div class="pcard-header" style="margin-bottom:20px;"> <div class="pcard-icon ic-teal">🔐</div> <div><div class="pcard-title">MissingCrypto Recovery Guide — $29.90</div><div class="pcard-sub">Complete step-by-step recovery · All major Australian exchanges</div></div> </div> <div class="premium-inner"> <div class="feature-list"> <div class="fi"><div class="fd">✓</div>CoinSpot, Binance, Coinbase, Swyftx & Independent Reserve recovery</div> <div class="fi"><div class="fd">✓</div>Hardware wallet & seed phrase recovery (Ledger & Trezor)</div> <div class="fi"><div class="fd">✓</div>What to do if your exchange has closed down</div> <div class="fi"><div class="fd">✓</div>ATO tax implications of recovered cryptocurrency</div> <div class="fi"><div class="fd">✓</div>Scam warning — how to avoid fake recovery services</div> <div class="fi"><div class="fd">✓</div>Printable crypto asset tracker · Lifetime access</div> </div> <div class="price-box"> <div class="price-label">One-time unlock</div> <div class="price-val">$29.90</div> <div class="price-note">One-time · Lifetime access</div> </div> </div> <div class="warn-box" style="margin-top:16px;"> ⚠️ <strong>Scam Warning:</strong> Never pay anyone a percentage or upfront crypto to recover your account. Legitimate exchanges never charge for account recovery. Our guide shows you how to do it yourself through official channels only. </div> <button class="btn btn-crypto" onclick="showModal()">🔓 Get The Recovery Guide — $29.90</button> <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:16px;margin-top:10px;font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);flex-wrap:wrap;"> <span>🔒 Secure via <strong style="color:var(--teal);">stripe</strong></span> <span>🛡️ 30-day money-back guarantee</span> </div> </div> </div> <div style="text-align:center;margin:8px 0 24px;font-size:15px;color:#aaa;font-style:italic;"> "Recovered $4,200 in Bitcoin from my old CoinSpot account using this guide!" – Verified Australian User </div> <div class="trust-bar"> <div class="ti"><div class="tdot"></div>Official exchange recovery only</div> <div class="ti"><div class="tdot"></div>No seed phrase required</div> <div class="ti"><div class="tdot"></div>No upfront crypto fees</div> <div class="ti"><div class="tdot"></div>Secure payment via Stripe</div> </div> </div> <footer> <span>🇦🇺 Not affiliated with any cryptocurrency exchange or government agency. Recovery guides based on publicly available exchange support processes.</span> <span>© 2025 MissingCash Australia · ABN 52 347 989 391 · <a href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection#83e2e7eeeaedc3eeeaf0f0eaede4e0e2f0ebade0eceeade2f6" style="color:var(--muted);"><span class="__cf_email__" data-cfemail="e48580898d8aa4898d97978d8a838785978cca878b89ca8591">[email&#160;protected]</span></a> · <a href="#home" style="color:var(--muted);">Back to MissingCash</a> · <a href="#privacy" style="color:var(--muted);">Privacy Policy</a></span> </footer> <!-- MODAL --> <div class="modal-overlay" id="cryptoModal"> <div class="modal-box"> <button class="modal-close" onclick="hideModal()">✕</button> <div class="modal-title">🔐 MissingCrypto Guide</div> <div class="modal-sub">Complete crypto recovery — step by step</div> <ul class="modal-features"> <li>CoinSpot, Binance, Coinbase, Swyftx & Independent Reserve recovery</li> <li>Hardware wallet & seed phrase recovery (Ledger & Trezor)</li> <li>What to do if your exchange has closed down</li> <li>ATO tax implications of recovered cryptocurrency</li> <li>Scam warning — avoid fake recovery services</li> <li>Printable crypto asset tracker · Lifetime access</li> </ul> <button class="btn btn-crypto" onclick="goStripe()">Buy Now — $29.90 One-Time</button> <div class="modal-secure">🔒 Secure via Stripe &nbsp;•&nbsp; 30-day money-back guarantee</div> </div> </div> <!-- CHAT --> <div class="chat-fab" onclick="toggleChat()">💬</div> <div class="chat-window" id="chatWindow"> <div class="chat-head"> <div class="chat-head-left"> <div class="chat-avatar">🤖</div> <div> <div class="chat-agent-name">Crypto Recovery Assistant</div> <div class="chat-online"><div class="online-dot"></div>Online now</div> </div> </div> <button class="chat-close-btn" onclick="toggleChat()">×</button> </div> <div class="chat-body" id="chatBody"> <div class="msg msg-bot"><div class="bot-av">🤖</div><div class="bubble">Hi! 👋 I can help you recover lost crypto. What exchange are you trying to recover from?</div></div> <div class="msg msg-user"><div class="bubble">CoinSpot — I forgot my password</div></div> <div class="msg msg-bot"><div class="bot-av">🤖</div><div class="bubble">Good news — CoinSpot has a solid recovery process. Our guide walks you through exactly what ID to submit and what to say to speed up the process. Most people recover access within 1-3 days.</div></div> </div> <div class="chat-input-row"> <input class="chat-input" id="chatInput" placeholder="Ask about crypto recovery..." onkeydown="sendChat(event)"> <button class="chat-send" onclick="sendChatMsg()">➤</button> </div> </div> <script data-cfasync="false" src="/cdn-cgi/scripts/5c5dd728/cloudflare-static/email-decode.min.js"></script><script> const STRIPE_URL = "https://buy.stripe.com/9B600iamo3Bz48d6I84c801"; const tickers = [ '"Recovered $4,200 in Bitcoin from my old CoinSpot account!" – Verified Australian User', '"Used this guide to recover my Binance account after losing my phone." – James T., VIC', '"Found $8,500 in ETH I thought was gone forever!" – Sarah M., NSW', '"Step-by-step guide made the whole process so easy." – Michael K., QLD', ]; let ti = 0; setInterval(()=>{ ti=(ti+1)%tickers.length; document.getElementById('tickerText').textContent=tickers[ti]; }, 5000); function showModal(){ document.getElementById('cryptoModal').classList.add('open'); document.body.style.overflow='hidden'; } function hideModal(){ document.getElementById('cryptoModal').classList.remove('open'); document.body.style.overflow=''; } function goStripe(){ window.open(STRIPE_URL,'_blank'); } function toggleChat(){ document.getElementById('chatWindow').classList.toggle('open'); } const botReplies=[ "Our guide covers CoinSpot, Binance, Coinbase, Swyftx and Independent Reserve — all step by step.", "You'll need photo ID, your registered email, and approximate account creation date. The guide explains exactly what to submit.", "Most exchange recoveries take 1-7 business days. Binance can take longer for complex cases.", "Hardware wallet recovery depends on whether you have your seed phrase. The guide covers both scenarios.", "Never pay anyone upfront to recover your crypto. All recoveries go through official exchange support channels.", "If your exchange has closed, Chapter 9 of the guide covers what to do — including closed Australian exchanges.", ]; let replyIdx=0; function sendChat(e){ if(e.key==='Enter') sendChatMsg(); } function sendChatMsg(){ const inp=document.getElementById('chatInput'); const msg=inp.value.trim(); if(!msg) return; const body=document.getElementById('chatBody'); body.innerHTML+=`<div class="msg msg-user"><div class="bubble">${msg}</div></div>`; inp.value=''; setTimeout(()=>{ body.innerHTML+=`<div class="msg msg-bot"><div class="bot-av">🤖</div><div class="bubble">${botReplies[replyIdx%botReplies.length]}</div></div>`; replyIdx++; body.scrollTop=body.scrollHeight; },900); body.scrollTop=body.scrollHeight; } </script>
