<div style="max-width:720px;margin:0 auto;padding:60px 20px 80px;">
  <h1 style="font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:2.8rem;color:#fff;margin-bottom:8px;">Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p style="font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:40px;">Last updated: January 2025 · ABN 52 347 989 391</p>
  
  <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:24px;">
    <div style="background:rgba(11,42,61,0.7);border:1px solid var(--navy-light);border-radius:16px;padding:24px;">
      <h2 style="font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:var(--gold);margin-bottom:12px;">1. Information We Collect</h2>
      <p style="font-size:14px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.7;">When you use our search function, we collect the name and optional details you enter solely to display simulated search results. We do not store this information on our servers. If you purchase our guide via Stripe, Stripe collects your payment details — we receive only a confirmation of your purchase, not your card information.</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background:rgba(11,42,61,0.7);border:1px solid var(--navy-light);border-radius:16px;padding:24px;">
      <h2 style="font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:var(--gold);margin-bottom:12px;">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p style="font-size:14px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.7;">We use Google Analytics to understand site usage in aggregate. We do not sell, rent or share your personal information with third parties for marketing purposes. Your email address (if provided) is used only to deliver your purchased guide.</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background:rgba(11,42,61,0.7);border:1px solid var(--navy-light);border-radius:16px;padding:24px;">
      <h2 style="font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:var(--gold);margin-bottom:12px;">3. Cookies</h2>
      <p style="font-size:14px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.7;">We use cookies for Google Analytics and to remember whether you have purchased our guide (via localStorage). You can disable cookies in your browser settings, though this may affect site functionality.</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background:rgba(11,42,61,0.7);border:1px solid var(--navy-light);border-radius:16px;padding:24px;">
      <h2 style="font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:var(--gold);margin-bottom:12px;">4. Data Security</h2>
      <p style="font-size:14px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.7;">We take reasonable steps to protect information. All payments are processed by Stripe using SSL encryption. We do not store credit card details.</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background:rgba(11,42,61,0.7);border:1px solid var(--navy-light);border-radius:16px;padding:24px;">
      <h2 style="font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:var(--gold);margin-bottom:12px;">5. Third Parties</h2>
      <p style="font-size:14px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.7;">We link to official Australian government sites (ATO, ASIC, AFCA, state revenue offices). We are not affiliated with any government agency. Payment processing is handled by Stripe. Analytics are handled by Google Analytics.</p>
